data.text:
King Henry I of France

Henry was born in 1005. He died at the age of 55 on August 4th, 1060.

Anne Agnesa of Kiev

Anne was born in 1036 in Kiev, Ukraine.

King Philippe (the Fair) of France I

Philippe, known as the Fair, was born about 1052. He died on July 29th, 1108.

Hugh ("le Grand") of Vermandois, Count of Vermandois

Hugh, known as le Grand, was born in 1057. He died at the age of 45 on October 18th, 1102.
